Greabe: As students of the same school, let us practice moderation and have manners in our relationships.
TL Note: Yamakan, the director of Kannagi, was previously sacked by Kyoto Animation after directing Lucky Star for 4 episodes.
Kyo-ani's official stand was that he has not reached the level of a director yet.
TS Note: On screen text is what he says.
TL-Note: Our beloved author of the Kannagi comic.
She is a Type-moon staff and is known for producing doujins of her group's work.
Well then, let us have her speak for one last time.
May you have Zange-chan's blessing tomorrow too!
Amazing, this is my first time meeting a celebrity!
What did you come here for?
We will not serve you tea.
Do not feel bothered by me.
I have no business with you today, Onee-sama.
The person I am looking for is...
I heard from Onee-sama that all you have been having is unhealthy food.
So I made some food for you.
Food that is high in nutritional value.
Why do not you chase Onee-sama out and live with me instead?
I am more caring than Onee-sama, and you get to eat...
What is with you, intruding on us like that?!
I will not allow such improper conduct for high school students!
Where am I to go if I get chased out?
Nagi-san, please do not treat Jin as an object!
Why do not the three of us have a match then?
Each of us will prepare today's dinner separately, and who does it best, wins.
Will not Zange-chan have the advantage?
There is no way we can win!
We stand a chance of winning.
Well then, let us go shopping.
Nagi-san, there is something I want to get from home.
How did I get myself into this?
Hakua, you have to do it yourself!
I am doing this for you!
Victory is mine for the taking.
I could have won if only Hakua had...
She is too honest of a person.
It is not that I cannot cook.
I do not cook only because it is too much trouble!
You can cook, yet you make me do it?
Because my sister is hopeless at tasting.
Flattering her like that after only seeing her once or twice!
The traffic counter is pretty high as well.
Only those close to her are kept in the dark.
I had boxed lunch together with Nagi-sama!
She is like a rare animal, she is so amusing!
Hey, is she really not a student in this school?
She is been saying she wants to participate in our physical education lessons,
so I lent her a set of P.E. attire!
Nobody found out since our physical education teacher is really irresponsible.
All of us helped her out, it was so fun!
She is somewhat of an occult freak?
She performed an exorcism for me.
She talked to a person like me so open-heartedly!
I have decided to follow her for life!
Thanks to Nagi-sama, I am finally qualified as a director.
Nagi-sama, please help me for the remaining episodes so that I do not get sacked.
Nagi-sama is the final goddess that has descend upon this defiled land!
With her delicious flat chest, We can finish three bowls of rice!
Nope, we can finish off any amount of rice!
Well, since she is neither in.jpg or paper format, it just does not get me going, you see!
Do not you think she is cute?
This does not look like a suspicious web page at all.
There are many female members anyway.
Club Regulation Clause 1: Do not pry into her private matters.
Clause 2: Do not impose on her residence.
And this is the important part.
Clause 3: Let it be your enjoyment for her to appear frequently in school and hide her from the teachers!
In other words, they are acting as bodyguards to protect her from teachers.
That is suspicious as it is!
The net has a high level of anonymity, after all.
It is even written here that I am her younger brother and Zange-chan is her younger sister.
This is clearly an invasion of privacy!
They are providing information so that others do not come digging for it.
I understand why you are so worked up, little brother.
You cannot help it, given how charismatic your sister is.
Secondly, her naivete tickles the protective instinct of other people!
Her erratic behavior is a refreshing change to the monotonous school life!
A locality limited only to the school is also good mania-ism!
Say, how do you know so much, Senpai?
Because I am a fan club member!
She is your sister after all.
Lately, I heard that there is an outsider hidden among our students.
Shall I call for a meeting, Suzushiro-sensei?
She is still a high school student, is not she?
Will not it suffice to catch her and just let her go with a warning?
But children nowadays do not know when to stop.
Depending on the situation, we may need to call the police.
Since when did you learn about the fan club?
Even if you ask me that...
It has an official name only because I gave them permission.
Why do you do such conspicuous things?
Do you even have a reason to go to school?
Of course I have my reasons!
There are impurities in the school.
I can handle it myself even when you are not around...
Do not do such dangerous things by yourself!
That is not the only reason.
Have you noticed any change about me?
They are thin to begin with.
Say any further and I will pull out your ahoge.
My powers seems to be increasing!
My powers as a god, that is!
I have told you before that I need to be idolized.
The students who are supporting me are giving me power.
Sooner or later, I will be able to use new powers!
There is a teacher over there, you would better not go there.
This is the first time I am seeing her.
She is much cuter in person!
I understand how Zange feels now!
Come with me for a minute.
Are you going to attack me again?
I have my purification staff with me today!
I can see that, so I will pass.
I will get to the point.
Are you not pleased because your territory has been taken away from you?
I am also a celebrity, so I have a special status within the school.
If you continue to do what you like, I will tell the teachers about you.
Why do not you just rat on me?
Why did not you do it?
Ah, it is officially known that we are sisters.
If I am caught, you will also be called in as a witness.
If that happens, I will feign ignorance to the end.
Then the students here are mine!
Do you think you can beat me without gathering a thousand fans?
But you look quite desperate though.
No matter how hard you try, I am still better at gathering people's devotion-
You are the girl who is been causing problems for us, are not you?
W-what do you mean by that, sir?
Have you mistaken me for somebody else?
Umm... that girl just now was my friend.
I did not come to talk about that matter.
Let me ask you a few questions.
That is right, first of all...
Is that body of yours borrowed from another person?
Is it true that she is inside?
Somebody else saw Hageshima, the counselor-in-charge, bringing her inside!
Nagi-sama will get driven out of school!
It is as you can see.
Are you sure she is inside?
I saw her with my own eyes!
Please do not worry about me.
My heart will always be with you.
That is the state she was in!
Even when she was the one in danger, she was still worried for us at the end!
Why are they like leaders of an anti-government organization?
If Nagi is caught, that means...
I will get a call at home since I am officially her brother.
Because my old man, who is our guardian, is not at home,
it will then go to Tsugumi's parents who are standing in as our guardians...
We have confirmed that you are not a student of this school.
Since when have you been doing this?
Where did you get that uniform?
May I know where is Suzushiro-sensei?
Please let me speak to him.
At the moment, he is talking with the principal about what to do with you.
It seems that she is undergoing a harsh interrogation.
According to the family register, you are not related in any way to Mikuriya Jin, supposedly your brother.
Have you been making up stories?
How should I lie my way out of this?
She is not causing any trouble for anyone!
I can use a new power!
Do not joke around at a time like this!
Then I cannot leave this place!
Such is the power of devotion!
It is completely reflecting off his head...
That is why I hate students!
All of you make fun of my head!
We are worried because you have not been coming for a while.
There has been quite a commotion after that incident...
It really got out of hand!
I do not want you to tell me that.
On that matter, are you looking at that homepage again?
They finally changed the rules too.
It is hard to believe that things has turned out like this.
Who would have thought she would become an official student of our school?
Nagi-sama, you are not one to talk.
It is unnatural that everything is going so smoothly.
Is there more than meets the eye?
Suzushiro-sensei has put in a good word for me.
First-year students may be unfamiliar with that name.
He is a teacher of religious studies.
He is a priest, and his family is said to be involved in the founding of the school.
I am doing research for religious studies and local history!
The thesis that I wrote a while back caught his attention.
Since it is an honor to have me here, he said he will let me enroll here!
A hidden prodigy has turned up in a place like this!
This should teach you not to look down on occult freaks!
Another one of her plausible yet far-fetched lies...
By the way, I am exempted from school fees!
Is this the result of gifted education?!
You do not have to be so wary of me.
Now that I know who you are, I cannot do anything to you.
I have no talents concerning the supernatural.
Now that I believe that you are a kind human, I will answer you truthfully.
I am not so wicked as to take the body of another human!
This body was legitimately made out of the earth and trees of Kannagi!
For a moment I thought you are with Zange-chan, but it seems I was wrong.
As I thought, you are related to Hakua in some way?
I understand that whatever is possessing my daughter's body is not evil.
Of course, that includes you too.
That girl has been desperately trying to hide things from me...
But I believe that my daughter's body should only belong to herself.
Hence I would like to free her if possible.
Is there an important purpose for your coming to school?
It is... a very, very important job.
I am putting my everything on the line for it.
But please take my word for it.
I will never do anything to harm the students.
What do you intend to do with Suzushiro Hakua?
I am going to free her, so that she can live a peaceful life with her father!
But in order to achieve that goal, I may need help from her father!
I am relieved to hear that.
It must be a pain to hide from the teachers.
Wait, can you really do that?
A private school is not only an education organization, but also a commercial one.
Well, just leave everything to me.
Is that really acceptable as a member of the church?
Or rather, you might just be a zealous father.
At least I did not notice before.
As a first-year student, how can I know all the minor details?
Takako knows more than you do.
Please do not put milk into your miso soup.
I do not want to be told off by someone who puts sauce on everything!
Ah geez, I should just go and live at Takako's place.
I know she will treat me nicely!
You do not have to go there, is not my house good enough?
I am the only family member here, so you can take it easy, right?
I am not complaining about you living here anyway...
Do not get so worked up.
Do not use it as a substitute for a torchlight!
Like for picking up coins dropped under a vending machine.
What did you come here for?
Well, I want to treat Jin-kun to a feast.
You are not the only one getting your territory invaded.
This has nothing to do with my parents!
Onee-sama, you are seriously an eyesore!
Watch the next episode of Kannagi too!
